Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:12.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}歡迎回到天堂與地獄的庭園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.56,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}白晝  夜晚  明天  後天  來回交替
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.56,0:01:18.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即使現在並無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:20.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}眯起看向現實的雙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:22.65,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}游魔之時已到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}甜蜜的安寧似同夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:28.19,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}面具下的愛也化作虛偽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.19,0:01:31.28,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}面對這難解的世界  難解的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.53,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只要我們心靈合一  或許就能找到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:36.08,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我並不是瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:39.91,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}各自行走的秒針所要抵達的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}是充滿笑聲還是淚水的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:44.50,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}互相遮掩住的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:46.75,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}就請你用捉迷藏的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:49.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}來找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不要妨礙我們
Comment: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:54.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}From the day we promised
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.03,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}漕ぎ始めた小さなボート
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:21:00.41,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Until we get to the place we dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.62,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}振り向かず along the way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.25,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}To go straight 息を揃え
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:08.00,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは同じ歌を歌う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.67,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}赤なら止まれ no rush
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.59,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Cuz it’s a long long way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:17.09,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Even if the heavy rain is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.93,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}We really don’t care
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.18,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾いた風も追い風に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.43,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いっそ遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:26.27,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The gate is open
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.89,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}遠ざかる skyline
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.52,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}動き出した life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:34.36,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The sunrise 登るまで seize the night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.57,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I keep dreaming of the day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:41.32,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Moonlit 僕らの描いた story
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.91,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Prove it その日までの journey
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:48.79,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How many miles can we go forward tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:10.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\bord1}How many miles can we go forward tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:54.07,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們立下誓言的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.03,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小小的木船駛向旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.03,0:21:00.41,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向著我們夢中的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:02.62,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無需留念  一心向前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:05.25,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}邁著相同的步子前行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:08.00,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們異口同聲地歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.67,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}紅燈就歇歇  不必著急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.59,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們要走的路還很長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:17.09,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使暴風雨將要到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.93,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我們也不會在意分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不如就乘上乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.43,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}飛向遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:26.27,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}門已經敞開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.89,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}無垠的天際線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.52,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}生命開始轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:34.36,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}抓住夜晚  跟隨日出的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:36.57,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我在夢中呼喚黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:41.32,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}月光灑下我們描繪的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.91,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}證明我們漫漫旅途的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:48.79,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今夜的我們  還能前進幾里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:10.48,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\bord1}今夜的我們  還能前進幾里？
